        <item>
            <title>1.8.3</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 15:46:56 +0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>64</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.8.3</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's New in 1.8.3</h2><ul></ul><p><strong>Added</strong></p><ul><li>✨ Added more naming-pattern title variants for filename formatting</li><li>🔄 Added `Check for Updates...` to the app menu</li></ul><p><strong>Improved</strong></p><ul><li>⚡ Improved monitor reliability around pause, retry, and watched-folder recovery</li><li>🛡️ Hardened Supabase edge functions, config loading, and Paddle processing</li><li>📊 Improved AI Rename progress messaging and drop-zone clarity</li></ul><p><strong>Fixed</strong></p><ul><li>🐛 Fixed monitor batches continuing after pause or connection loss</li><li>🩹 Fixed retry and undo flows so reverted files can be processed again</li><li>📂 Fixed watched-folder handling when monitored folders are deleted or unavailable</li><li>🔧 Fixed same-name renames failing in monitor and activity flows</li></ul>
]]></description>
